## ðŸ§  7. Advanced Concepts

| Concept               | Description & Use Case                                                  |
|-----------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| ðŸ§® **Nested UDFs**     | Call one UDF inside another for layered logic                          |
| ðŸ§¾ **UDF in WHERE**    | Use scalar UDFs to filter rows dynamically                             |
| ðŸ“Š **UDF in JOIN**     | Use table-valued UDFs as virtual tables                                |
| ðŸ§© **Parameter Defaults** | Set default values for optional logic                                 |
| ðŸš€ **Performance Tips** | Avoid scalar UDFs in large joins; prefer iTVFs for optimizer support   |

